the longest yard may refer to :   the longest yard ( 1974 film ) , starring burt reynolds   mean machine , a 2001 football ( soccer ) adaptation starring vinnie jones   the longest yard ( 2005 film ) , remake of the 1974 film starring adam sandler and chris rock   the longest yard ( soundtrack ) , soundtrack for the 2005 remake .

movie trivia : actor who captained " the mean machine " in " the longest yard "

burt reynolds